{"tid":753764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[殘體慎入] 堅決抵制西方\"司法獨立\"等錯誤思潮影響","createTime":"2018-07-24T01:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T03:39:48.000Z","uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d19f9ad415170966f186ff068ad831cfd2372eb","tid":753764,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>厲害了我的國</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4064324501055065?wm=3333_2001&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4064324501055065%3Fwm%3D3333_2001%26sourcetype%3Dweixin%26from%3Dsinglemessage%26isappinstalled%3D0&d=J2irMVgUbvGxlRYH3ktlejPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0990fbcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4064324501055065?wm=3333_2001&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【坚决抵制西方&ldquo;司法独立&rdquo;等错误思潮影响】坚决抵制西方&ldquo;宪政民主&rdquo;、&ldquo;三权分立&rdquo;、&ldquo;司法独立&rdquo;等错误思潮影响，坚定不移走中国特色社会主义法治道路，是旗帜鲜明地表明了我们坚决拥护中国共产党领导的决心。国家审判机关只有在坚持党的领导的前提下，依法独立行使审判权，坚决抵制西方&ldquo;司法独立&rdquo;，才可称之为人民法院，才能充分发挥其在社会主义经济发展中的重要作用，并为逐步缩小我国同世界先进水平的差距、在社会主义基础上实现中华民族伟大复兴做出新的更大贡献！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/092545_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F092545_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=f481ca2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"500bdfe2d04276ed808dadf72216abfb8d99c560","tid":753764,"uid":11962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:28:31.000Z","msg":"依法治國會迷失方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873aa87abdf0ce64cc1278807fc9fdca56c64ae7","tid":753764,"uid":50745